6713100304.streakfaq:
Here is everything you need to know about our Wheel/Streak Promotion!

Spin a wheel for every seven days of your streak! There will be five wheels that are cycled throughout your journey!


Track your streak with our custom Telegram bot: @rt_streak_tracker_bot 

Type /Lookup into the bot to see: 

✅ 1. Your current streak 

✅ 2. The time of your wheel spin if a milestone is reached (milestones: 7, 14, 21, or 28-day streaks)

✅ 3. The day you lost your streak, if applicable 

✅ 4. Your highest streak 

✅ 5. If you revived your streak after losing it 

Wheel Spin Notifications:

✅ You'll be notified early in the day of your scheduled spin 

✅ Admin spins the wheel for you at a specified time for fairness 

✅ You can confirm your spin time using the /lookup command 

Data updates the morning after: 

✅ If you play 100+ hands today, your streak will update tomorrow 

For example: if you play 100 hands on a Wednesday the streak will be updated at 9:00 am Thursday.

✅ If you'd like to check your hand count for the current day, feel free to send us a message.


✅ Questions? Just reach out to us! 

For prize details, announcements, and more, join our channel:
 
https://t.me/+QcPI0RvGGI1lMGIx
